{"product_id":"madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA PEEL Brightening AHA Peel mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eGive your skin an instant radiance boost with this active AHA peeling mask. Formulated with nature’s superdose of active acids, this mask ensures multiple skincare benefits: Removes the dead cells to uncover smoother, more radiant skin surface, exfoliates to stimulate cell turnover and regeneration, brightens the complexion and diminishes appearance of age-spots and fine lines, helps to unclog pores and improves the absorption and effect of other cosmetic products. Especially beneficial for dull, tired skin with signs of aging, lines, wrinkles, age-spots, lack of glow, clogged pores and acne.\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e ​Apply to clean skin, leave on for 3–10 minutes. Rinse off thoroughly, follow with a toner and moisturiser of your choice.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Lactic Acid, Glycerin, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Water, Galactoarabinan, Potassium Hydroxide, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Glucomannan, Mica (CI 77019), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Aroma, Cellulose gum, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Fruit Extract, Sambucus Nigra (Elder) Flower Extract, Ethyl Lauroyl Arginate HCl, Xanthan Gum, Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916404298055,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml-412418.jpg?v=1739897193","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}